Third-party notices
===================

This project does **not** bundle third-party weights or code, but at runtime
it interoperates with the following:

- **SegFormer face-parsing checkpoint** (``jonathandinu/face-parsing`` on
  HuggingFace) — released under the **Apache License 2.0**. Downstream users
  must retain its notice when redistributing.

- **BiSeNet CelebAMask-HQ checkpoint** (e.g. ``zllrunning/face-parsing.PyTorch``
  or a drop-in equivalent) — released under **MIT**. Users load their own
  checkpoint; this project does not ship it.

- **transformers** (``huggingface/transformers``) — **Apache 2.0**.
- **torch** — **BSD-3-Clause** (and component-specific licences).
- **opencv-python** — **Apache 2.0** (with third-party notices).
- **numpy** — **BSD-3-Clause**. **Pillow** — **HPND**.

Check each project's own LICENSE file for the authoritative terms.
